This is Perl module Alien::ChromeDriver.

INSTALLATION

Type the following command:

    $ curl -L http://cpanmin.us | perl - Alien::ChromeDriver

Or install cpanm and then run the following command to install
Alien::ChromeDriver:

    $ cpanm Alien::ChromeDriver

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf Alien-chromedriver-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd Alien-chromedriver-$version
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

Alien::ChromeDriver documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc Alien::ChromeDriver

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

